			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">To start this off I play a lvl 65 Mage on Luclin VT keyed, Time Flagged and Qvic flagged so I know what im talking about... I would think ( my opinion =D ). 
<br />

<br />
      At this point in EQ I dont understand why anyone would want to play a Mage...their dps lacks in the highend game...our nukes are, ya they suck. Think back to yourself and think of the highest crit u have had with your Mage. In the 4500 range? ya thats horrible considering a DRUID can do the same damn thing.
<br />

<br />
      Our pets, well they suck atm also. Soloing we cant handle anything From BoT and above and anything lower than that isnt worth soloing in so those zones dont matter. During raids what is the point of having a pet out? To get our extra 5m a tick from it then destroy it? Or is it there to train the raid when u get lazy and forget to hit /hold because in Battle it does little or no dmg. In Qvic and other zones the AoE put off by the Named kill the pet before it is even capable of doing any dmg and why heal it that just takes away from our slack ass nukes. 
<br />

<br />
      Mod rods, Who honestly cares about mod rods anymore. They nerfed them horribly, and the only time a decent player is going to need them is if the fight lasts longer than 5-10min and they are chain casting heals or nukes. Most players forget about them anyways so when mass mod rod comes around they just actually remember that they had one and say "oops."
<br />

<br />
     CoH, Why would anyone want to stand around waiting for people to zi to a zone so they can be thier bitch and teleport them across the zone? This is one of the best thing Mages have and it does nothing for them except waste there time and money.
<br />

<br />
    Soloing...Mages have no defensive skills, our pets lack. and our pet heals arent worth casting its better to chain cast pets during there enrage period lol, and its not like we are fabulous at crowd control so if an add comes along that is actually capable of doing a little damage we are screwed...again.
<br />

<br />
    
<br />
       Thats really all I have to complain about hehe. I would like to apologize for the post but I am really pissed off about what they have done to my favorite class in the game. In the beginning they were worth while to play. Now they are obsolete.
<br />

<br />
