			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I played EQ from 4 years ago (with some breaks)... I started a monk, but he did not fill my game needs, just push A and 5 every 6s... is not my idea of fun.
<br />

<br />
Then I made a druid... he ran oom in no time (yes, I put my points in CHA, and not in WIS, and was human, but who cares?), and the benefits of his all-purpose skills were not enough for me. Then I played rogues for 2 years... impressive DPS. Almost noticeable DPS... but hey! I hate being /LFG for hours... not much time to play, I want not to waste it LFGing...
<br />

<br />
I played all classes of this game, and only found three classes who could solo well (with my skills):
<br />
-druid
<br />
-necro
<br />
-mage
<br />
(I will forget the bard... running in circles singing while your train tries to kill you while you try to charm them is not my idea of fun)
<br />

<br />
DRUID:
<br />
SoW, ports, nice DoTs, heals, charms... is awesome class, but snare-root-dot-dot-dot-nuke-nuke-loot is not my idea of fun... rinse-repeat
<br />

<br />
NECRO:
<br />
omg! incredible pet! taps! ubah dots! more pet! more taps! FEIGN DEAD!! (this is the skill/spell i want for me). Is like a mage, and could fit in any place solo, in a group, in a raid...
<br />

<br />
MAGE:
<br />
omg! incredible pet(s)! nukes! more nukes! more pets! more nukes!
<br />

<br />
I though the mage and the necro were my classes...why I am a mage and not a necro? will sound stupid... SUMMON FOOD, SUMMON WATER
<br />

<br />
I'm sorry... I'm too lazy to remember to buy my own food nor water. And dirt my hands carving for bones is for sad ppl...
<br />

<br />
As a mage, I can summon stuff (and now not only for me, Fluffy is happy with his toys), call Fluffy and, if he is free, go to do some funny things.
<br />

<br />
I'm not the best nuker in the game, but I love to see all these flames around my enemies.
<br />
Fluffy is not the best pet of the game (nothing like an ogre warrior to be your pet), but I love him in all his forms (earth, air, water, fire and the lovely hability to disguiss like any mob in zone).
<br />
Yes, my blade of kedge is not a blade of carnage, but Fluffy likes cool using it.
<br />
My DoTs sux, my heals sux, my defense sux, but playing a mage is the funniest thing I did in EQ (except kill a friend with an accidental DoT in my youth when I was playing in RZ server).
<br />

<br />
Never had care about the high end game. I'm 65, have 42AA and some nice gear (not EP nor VT, but nice) and I can do anything solo (well, with Fluffy). All these things you will say I cannot do solo, is only because I want not to do.
<br />

<br />
Obsolete? I don't think so...maybe we fell down in the DPS ranking, but think seriously... almost our epic is not a dead duck's head in the top of a stick.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
